inistered with a moderate inhibitor of CYP450 3A4.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/92512/', '', 'Propafenone, Tocainide, Procainamide, Mexiletine, Disopyramide, Bretylium, Moricizine, Ibutilide', 'Ciclesonide, Umeclidinium, Mometasone furoate, Aclidinium, Glycopyrronium, Flunisolide, Ipratropium, Cromoglicic acid, Betamethasone, Revefenacin, Nedocromil, More', 1767369485);
